{"body":"<div><div id=\"having\"><div class=\"hue-doc-title\">HAVING Clause</div><div><p>\n      Performs a filter operation on a <span class=\"hue-doc-codeph\">SELECT</span> query, by examining the results of aggregation\n      functions rather than testing each individual table row. Therefore, it is always used in conjunction with a\n      function such as <span class=\"hue-doc-codeph\"><a class=\"hue-doc-internal-link\" href=\"javascript:void(0);\" data-doc-ref=\"topics/impala_count.xml\" data-doc-anchor-id=\"count\">COUNT()</a></span>,\n      <span class=\"hue-doc-codeph\"><a class=\"hue-doc-internal-link\" href=\"javascript:void(0);\" data-doc-ref=\"topics/impala_sum.xml\" data-doc-anchor-id=\"sum\">SUM()</a></span>,\n      <span class=\"hue-doc-codeph\"><a class=\"hue-doc-internal-link\" href=\"javascript:void(0);\" data-doc-ref=\"topics/impala_avg.xml\" data-doc-anchor-id=\"avg\">AVG()</a></span>,\n      <span class=\"hue-doc-codeph\"><a class=\"hue-doc-internal-link\" href=\"javascript:void(0);\" data-doc-ref=\"topics/impala_min.xml\" data-doc-anchor-id=\"min\">MIN()</a></span>, or\n      <span class=\"hue-doc-codeph\"><a class=\"hue-doc-internal-link\" href=\"javascript:void(0);\" data-doc-ref=\"topics/impala_max.xml\" data-doc-anchor-id=\"max\">MAX()</a></span>, and typically with the\n      <span class=\"hue-doc-codeph\"><a class=\"hue-doc-internal-link\" href=\"javascript:void(0);\" data-doc-ref=\"topics/impala_group_by.xml\" data-doc-anchor-id=\"group_by\">GROUP BY</a></span> clause also.\n    </p><p id=\"restrictions_blurb\"><b>Restrictions:</b></p><p>\n      The filter expression in the <span class=\"hue-doc-codeph\">HAVING</span> clause cannot include a scalar subquery.\n    </p><p id=\"related_info\"><b>Related information:</b></p><p><a class=\"hue-doc-internal-link\" href=\"javascript:void(0);\" data-doc-ref=\"topics/impala_select.xml\" data-doc-anchor-id=\"select\">SELECT Statement</a>,\n      <a class=\"hue-doc-internal-link\" href=\"javascript:void(0);\" data-doc-ref=\"topics/impala_group_by.xml\" data-doc-anchor-id=\"group_by\">GROUP BY Clause</a>,\n      <a class=\"hue-doc-internal-link\" href=\"javascript:void(0);\" data-doc-ref=\"topics/impala_aggregate_functions.xml\" data-doc-anchor-id=\"aggregate_functions\">Impala Aggregate Functions</a></p></div></div></div>","title":"HAVING Clause"}